<plot>Echo is a story of lost love and the impact it has on those who are left behind. An old man, Albert visits the beach where he and his late wife Lily first became sweethearts and is lost in the loneliness of remembering the past. Whilst on his usual pilgrimage to Lily's grave he meets two teenagers, one of whom Albert underestimates.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?165065</url></doc>
